    },
    {
      "time": 186.1,
      "time_str": "03:06.100",
      "text": "将一切都体谅将一切都原谅",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 189.2,
      "time_str": "03:09.200",
      "text": "我尝试找答案而答案很简单",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 192.8,
      "time_str": "03:12.800",
      "text": "简单得很遗憾",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 195.06,
      "time_str": "03:15.060",
      "text": "因为成长我们逼不得已要习惯",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 201.67,
      "time_str": "03:21.670",
      "text": "因为成长我们忽尔间说散就散",
